---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — AtLeast"
  description="AtLeast collects no personal data. The app runs entirely on your device."
>
  <section class="px-6 py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="mb-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mb-12 text-sm text-brand-muted">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-muted">
        <p>
          AtLeast collects no personal data. The app operates entirely on-device.
        </p>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-brand-text">Data we do not collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-1">
            <li>No analytics or usage tracking</li>
            <li>No crash reporting sent off-device</li>
            <li>No personal identifiers</li>
            <li>No location data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-brand-text">Data stored locally</h2>
          <p>
            Timer settings (duration, tap interval) are stored in UserDefaults on your Apple Watch only. This data never leaves your device.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-brand-text">Third parties</h2>
          <p>
            None. AtLeast has no third-party SDKs, analytics, or advertising.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-brand-text">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about this policy? Email us at
            <a href="mailto:support@atleastapp.com" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">
              support@atleastapp.com
            </a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
